criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  Patients treated with HD or HDF since >6 weeks, 3 times a week;

  -  Patients able to understand the study procedures;

  -  Patients willing to provide written informed consent.

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  Current age < 18 years;

  -  Severe incompliance to dialysis procedure and accompanying prescriptions (frequency
     and duration of dialysis treatment and fluid restriction);

  -  Life expectancy < 3 months due to non-renal disease.
